{"word":"ὀξυθυμέω","slug":"ὀξυθυμέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὀξυθυμέω</b></el> <el>(ὀξῠθῡμέω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>ὀξύθῡμος</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be quick to anger</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be provoked</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}